### [Moapa Valley National Wildlife Refuge](/Moapa_Valley_National_Wildlife_Refuge)

[IUCN category](/IUCN_protected_area_categories) IV (habitat/species management area)

*A view of the [Moapa Valley Wildlife Refuge](/Moapa_Valley_National_Wildlife_Refuge), looking north. One might almost imagine a semblance of peace, if one were so inclined.*

